This is my project on neural nets. Currently it brings following files:
ELECTRO_BRAIN.cpp///////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Source code for example executable utilising provided headers.
TNET.h//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Header defining following structures:
- TNeuron,
- TLayer,
- TNet
TFILTER.h////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Header definign following structures:
- TFilter_bas(abstract struct),
- TFilter_yes,
- TFilter_high(to be worked on).
TSAMPLE.h////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Header definign following structures and functions:
- TSample,
- normalize.
DEITIES, DEITIES_A////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Sample data files, defining random-generated deities, defined by mythological threads, present or not, in their mythus.
CONF///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Example configuration file, input for compiled ELECTRO_BRAIN:

sample	DEITIES	/*take "DEITIES" file as sample for net learning*/
analys	DEITIES_A /*take "DEITIES_A" file as sample for analysis but no for net learning*/
LAY	1 /*construct net with 1 layer*/
struct	manual /*manual net architecture*/
	sig sig sig sig sig sig sig sig eoN /*the layer will have 8 neuron with "sig"[sigmoid] activation function*/
learn	unsu /*"unsu" unsupervised learning mode - only available at the moment*/
filter_yes	/*definition of filters_yes: only datasets having non-zero values at target signal will be used for target neuron learning*/
	0 0	LORD eoF	
	0 1	SEER eoF	
	0 2	WARRIOR eoF
	0 3	MOTHER_EARTH eoF
	
	0 4	MOUNTAIN WHITE eoF
	0 5	SEA	BLUE eoF	/*use only samples having non-zero values at 'SEA' and 'BLUE' channels for learning of neuron 5 from layer 0*/
	0 6	FOREST	DOE eoF
	0 7	BLACK RED eoF
	-1	/*end of yes-filters definition*/
filter_no	/*definition of filters_no: datasets having non-zero values at target signal will not be used for target neuron learning*/
	0 4	BLACK eoF	/*do not use samples having non-zero values at 'BLACK' channel for learning of neuron 1 from layer 0*/
	0 5	RED eoF
	0 6	EAGLE eoF
	0 7	WHITE eoF
	-1	/*end of yes-filters definition*/
cycle	300	/*number of learning cycles*/
save	RES	/*name of analysis results saving file*/
EOF	/*end of file label*/
